name: Generator Vol. 1
overview: Generator Vol. 1 is a demo disc containing preview versions of various Sega Dreamcast games released in 1999 It was only available in North America as was bundled with early Dreamcast consoles. Playable Demos - Ready 2 Rumble Boxing, Power Stone, Monaco Grand Prix, The House of the Dead 2, Sonic Adventure, Sega Bass Fishing, Flag to Flag
